Description: Provides an extensible framework for training artificial neural networks using metaheuristic, gradient-based, and hybrid optimization algorithms. The package supports feed-forward multilayer perceptrons for regression and classification tasks, customizable activation functions, loss functions, performance metrics, preprocessing options, and general-purpose continuous optimization.
